<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Ferrari SF90 Stradale Guide</title>
  <style>
    /* General Styles */
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f5f5, #d3d3d3);
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      color: #333;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background: #fff;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      border-radius: 10px;
    }

    h1, h2 {
      color: #c82333; /* Red */
    }

    h1 {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      margin-top: 30px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      padding-bottom: 10px;
      border-bottom: 3px solid #c82333; /* Red */
      display: inline-block;
    }

    p, ul {
      line-height: 1.8;
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: #555;
    }

    ul {
      list-style-type: disc;
      padding-left: 20px;
    }

    li {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    /* Card Styles */
    .card {
      background: #f8f9fa; /* Light Grey */
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      padding: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    }

    .card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }

    /* Images Section */
    .images {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-around;
      margin: 20px 0;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .images img {
      max-width: 45%;
      height: auto;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .images img:hover {
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    /* Video Section */
    .video-container {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding: 20px;
      background: #f8f9fa; /* Light Grey */
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .video-container iframe {
      max-width: 100%;
      height: 400px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      border: 5px solid #c82333; /* Red */
    }

    /* Responsive Design */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .images img {
        max-width: 100%;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }

      .video-container iframe {
        height: 250px;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }

      h2 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Ferrari SF90 Stradale Guide</h1>

    <!-- Overview Section -->
    <div class="card">
      <h2>Overview</h2>
      <p>The Ferrari SF90 Stradale is a groundbreaking plug-in hybrid supercar that combines cutting-edge technology with Ferrari's legendary performance. Itâ€™s the first series-production Ferrari to feature a plug-in hybrid powertrain, offering a perfect blend of power, efficiency, and innovation.</p>
    </div>
<!-- Images Section -->
    <div class="images">
      <img src="https://cdn.ferrari.com/cms/network/media/img/resize/5cee922e80b248729778dddf-d-interni-02?" alt="Ferrari SF90 Stradale Image 2">
    </div>
    <!-- Key Features Section -->
    <div class="card">
      <h2>Key Features</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Hybrid Powertrain:</strong> Combines a 4.0-liter twin-turbocharged V8 engine with three electric motors, delivering a combined output of 986 horsepower.</li>
        <li><strong>All-Wheel Drive:</strong> The electric motors power the front wheels, making it Ferrari's first all-wheel-drive sports car.</li>
        <li><strong>Lightweight Design:</strong> Features advanced materials like carbon fiber and aluminum to keep weight low and performance high.</li>
        <li><strong>Electric-Only Mode:</strong> Can travel up to 15 miles (25 km) on electric power alone, making it ideal for city driving.</li>
        <li><strong>Aerodynamics:</strong> Incorporates advanced aerodynamic features, including a rear spoiler and active flaps, to optimize performance and stability.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Performance Section -->
    <div class="card">
      <h2>Performance</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>0-60 mph:</strong> 2.5 seconds.</li>
        <li><strong>Top Speed:</strong> 211 mph (340 km/h).</li>
        <li><strong>Power Output:</strong> 986 horsepower.</li>
        <li><strong>Torque:</strong> 590 lb-ft.</li>
        <li><strong>Transmission:</strong> 8-speed dual-clutch automatic.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
	<!-- Video Section -->
    <div class="video-container">
      <h2>Learn More About the Ferrari SF90 Stradale</h2>
      <iframe width="560" height="315" 
        src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/MvVXL-vBQs0" 
        frameborder="0" 
        allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" 
        allowfullscreen>
      </iframe>
    </div>

    <!-- Technology Section -->
    <div class="card">
      <h2>Technology</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Manettino Dial:</strong> Offers four driving modes, including Electric, Hybrid, Performance, and Qualify, to optimize performance and efficiency.</li>
        <li><strong>Regenerative Braking:</strong> Captures energy during braking to recharge the battery.</li>
        <li><strong>Infotainment System:</strong> Features a 16-inch digital instrument cluster and a touchscreen interface for seamless control.</li>
        <li><strong>Advanced Driver Aids:</strong> Includes adaptive cruise control, lane-keeping assist, and a 360-degree camera system.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    

    
  </div>
</body>
</html>